title: The Incredible Adventures of Van Helsing Update v1.3.3b Incl 7DL
description:
The Incredible Adventures of Van Helsing Update v1.3.3b Incl 7DLC

Extract 7zip over v1.3.1 or later & play!


The Incredible Adventures Of Van Helsing v1.3.3b

Major changes include:

Fixed bugs:

    Fixed a bug where players could not attack with controller buttons. 

Multiplayer:

    You can now host Neverending story from server creator.
